article.headline: Boone scores 16, UNLV beats Hofstra 74-56
article.description: — Keylan Boone had 16 points in UNLV's 74-56 victory over Hofstra on Thursday.
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Keylan Boone had 16 points in UNLV's 74-56 victory over Hofstra on Thursday. Boone also contributed five rebounds for the Rebels (5-5). Luis Rodriguez added 15 points and had 10 rebounds. Jackie Johnson III also had 10 points. Darlinstone Dubar led the way for the Pride (7-5) with 17 points. Hofstra also got 13 points, four assists and two steals from Tyler Thomas. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
